  "skillContent": "<p><span style=\"color: #666666\">设计与交互: </span><strong>Photoshop, Illustrator, InDesign</strong> (数字图像处理、矢量图设计、排版), <strong>Figma</strong> (组件库构建、响应式交互原型)</p><p><span style=\"color: #666666\">游戏开发: </span><strong>Unity</strong> (Shader Graph着色器开发、Timeline 序列动画、UI Canvas、Tilemap 关卡构建), <strong>Unreal Engine</strong> (蓝图、材质编辑器), <strong>Spine</strong> (2D 骨骼动画、状态机配置), <strong>Houdini</strong> (正在学习)</p><p><span style=\"color: #666666\">3D 建模与制造: </span><strong>Maya, Blender</strong> (高低模、UV 拆分 、纹理贴图), <strong>3D Printing</strong> (切片、支撑结构优化)</p><p><span style=\"color: #666666\">Web开发: </span><strong>HTML5, CSS3</strong> (响应式架构、交互式前端开发), <strong>P5.js</strong> (基于javascript的创意编程), <strong>GitHub</strong> (Git 版本控制、协同开发)</p><p><span style=\"color: #666666\">影视后期与动效: </span><strong>After Effects</strong> (图形动效、特效合成、粒子系统), <strong>Premiere Pro</strong> (剪辑、调色等)</p>",
  "selfEvaluationContent": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">热爱游戏，熟练掌握各种设计软件；善于主动学习，积极尝试探索新的领域；擅长团队协作。</span></p>",
